### USERS ###

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8000/api/users
Accept: application/ld+json

### Get specific user
GET http://localhost:8000/api/users/1
Accept: application/ld+json

### Create new user
POST http://localhost:8000/api/users
Content-Type: application/ld+json

{
  "email": "nouveau@test.fr",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Jean",
  "lastName": "Nouveau"
}

### Update user
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/ld+json

{
  "email": "test@groupup.fr",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Jean",
  "lastName": "Dupont Modifié"
}

### TEAMS ###

### Get all teams
GET http://localhost:8000/api/teams
Accept: application/ld+json

### Get specific team
GET http://localhost:8000/api/teams/1
Accept: application/ld+json

### Create new team
POST http://localhost:8000/api/teams
Content-Type: application/ld+json

{
  "name": "Nouvelle Team",
  "description": "Description de la team",
  "creator": "/api/users/1"
}

### EVENTS ###

### Get all events
GET http://localhost:8000/api/events
Accept: application/ld+json

### Create new event
POST http://localhost:8000/api/events
Content-Type: application/ld+json

{
  "title": "Nouvel Événement",
  "description": "Description de l'événement",
  "proposedDate": "2024-03-15T19:00:00+00:00",
  "location": "Strasbourg",
  "team": "/api/teams/1",
  "createdBy": "/api/users/1"
}

### MEMBERSHIPS ###

### Get all memberships
GET http://localhost:8000/api/memberships
Accept: application/ld+json

### Add member to team
POST http://localhost:8000/api/memberships
Content-Type: application/ld+json

{
  "member": "/api/users/2",
  "team": "/api/teams/1",
  "role": "member"
}

### PARTICIPATIONS ###

### Get all participations
GET http://localhost:8000/api/participations
Accept: application/ld+json

### Add participation to event
POST http://localhost:8000/api/participations
Content-Type: application/ld+json

{
  "participant": "/api/users/1",
  "event": "/api/events/1",
  "status": "present"
}

